<div class="customrounded box2 light80 title2"  >
	<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br />Quebec's National Shrines (Canada)&nbsp;</h3>
<p><img src="/images/stories/accueil/sanctuaires.gif" alt="sanctuaires" style="display: block; float: left; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;" height="121" width="120" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #61736a; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; text-align: -webkit-auto; font-size: 10pt;">The province of Quebec is rich in four of the five major national shrines designated by the Conference of Catholic Bishops of Canada.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #8c401e; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><a href="http://www.quebecshrines.com/index.php"><span style="color: #ba6647;">Click here</span></a></span></span><span style="color: #8c401e; font-size: 10pt;"><span style="color: #ba6647; font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></span></p></div>
